IO::Util README File
====================


Description
-----------

This is a micro-weight module that exports a few functions of general utility in IO operations.
  
    
Installation
------------

1. CPAN installation

    perl -MCPAN -e 'install IO::Util'


2. Standard installation
- from the directory where this file is located, type:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

